    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "酒館挑戰",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "友好對局·翠翎恐蕈的巡遊",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「喵嗚...」「據說在幽林的深處，有處於蕈獸頂點的偉大存在...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【特殊規則】「翠翎恐蕈」免疫凍結、眩暈、石化。初始裝備有天賦牌「孢子增殖」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3199,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/920c7d546361d0b52dd95613517319f9_6116404733914419935.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "翠翎恐蕈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "（此模式下的翠翎恐蕈生命值為36）",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "解鎖要求",
                      "type": "text"
